<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 12:29:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大阪因背部受伤退出日本公开赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/osaka-pulls-out-japan-open-with-back-injury-2024-10-07/</link><description>组织者周一表示，前世界排名第一的大阪娜奥米因背部受伤而退出日本公开赛，这迫使她上周退出中国公开赛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 11:31:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/osaka-pulls-out-japan-open-with-back-injury-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巨额就业人数令 10 年期国债收益率突破 4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-07/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着地区紧张局势的加剧，菲律宾与盟国举行海军演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-launches-naval-drills-with-allies-regional-tensions-simmer-2024-10-07/</link><description>菲律宾、美国和其他四个国家的武装部队开始在菲律宾北部吕宋岛面向台湾的海岸举行联合海军演习，以在与中国的紧张局势升级之际展示海军实力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-launches-naval-drills-with-allies-regional-tensions-simmer-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>对冲基金 Elliott 对驳回 LME 镍诉讼的上诉败诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hedge-fund-elliott-loses-appeal-against-dismissal-lme-nickel-lawsuit-2024-10-07/</link><description>对冲基金埃利奥特联合公司(Elliott Associates)周一在其针对伦敦金属交易所(London Metal Exchange)就取消的价值数十亿美元的镍交易提起的诉讼被驳回的上诉中败诉，法官表示，这对整个市场的稳定至关重要。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hedge-fund-elliott-loses-appeal-against-dismissal-lme-nickel-lawsuit-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>以色列特使称寻呼机爆炸事件引起台湾“关注”，双边关系牢固</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/exploding-pagers-got-attention-taiwan-bilateral-ties-strong-israel-envoy-says-2024-10-07/</link><description>以色列驻台北特使周一表示，与一家台湾公司有关的黎巴嫩寻呼机爆炸事件引起了台湾的关注，但以色列与台湾的关系牢固，基于共同价值观和良好的沟通渠道。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/exploding-pagers-got-attention-taiwan-bilateral-ties-strong-israel-envoy-says-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康与香港上市公司石药集团签署价值 19.2 亿美元的许可协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-19-bln-licensing-deal-with-hk-listed-cspc-2024-10-07/</link><description>阿斯利康周一表示，将根据独家许可协议向石药集团有限公司支付高达 19.2 亿美元，以增强这家英瑞制药商的心血管产品线。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 08:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-19-bln-licensing-deal-with-hk-listed-cspc-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>古德温：波波维奇的“获胜心态”可以帮助澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovics-winning-mentality-can-help-australia-goodwin-2024-10-07/</link><description>边锋克雷格·古德温表示，澳大利亚球员对格雷厄姆·阿诺德辞去教练职务感到难过，但希望在托尼·波波维奇的“胜利心态”下取得进步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovics-winning-mentality-can-help-australia-goodwin-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>《刺客信条》制作商育碧表示在收购报告后定期审查选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ubisoft-says-it-reviews-strategic-options-shares-rise-2024-10-07/</link><description>《刺客信条》、《孤岛惊魂》和《看门狗》视频游戏的制造商育碧周一表示，它会定期审查“所有战略选择”，但拒绝就最近的收购兴趣报告发表进一步评论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/ubisoft-says-it-reviews-strategic-options-shares-rise-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>联合国称 Telegram 应用程序为东南亚犯罪团伙提供“地下市场”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/criminal-networks-southeast-asia-flourish-telegrams-underground-markets-un-says-2024-10-07/</link><description>联合国周一在一份报告中表示，东南亚强大的犯罪网络广泛使用通讯应用程序 Telegram，该应用程序从根本上改变了有组织犯罪进行大规模非法活动的方式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/criminal-networks-southeast-asia-flourish-telegrams-underground-markets-un-says-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国可能在国家主席发表全国讲话后在台湾周围发动军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-likely-launch-military-drills-around-taiwan-after-presidents-national-2024-10-07/</link><description>台湾官员称，中国本周可能在台湾附近举行军事演习，以台湾总统赖清德即将发表的国庆讲话为借口，向台湾施压，要求其接受其主权主张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-likely-launch-military-drills-around-taiwan-after-presidents-national-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>印尼顾问称普拉博沃将于下月访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-next-month-says-adviser-2024-10-07/</link><description>印度尼西亚当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 的高级顾问周一表示，他将于下个月访问中国，会见投资者，并邀请他们参与一个巨型海堤项目。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-visit-china-next-month-says-adviser-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫穆伊祖与印度莫迪承诺加强合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/maldives-president-muizzu-meet-indias-modi-amid-economic-woes-2024-10-07/</link><description>马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖和印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周一举行会谈，新德里承诺在这个岛国从经济危机中复苏之际加强战略合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 04:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/maldives-president-muizzu-meet-indias-modi-amid-economic-woes-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>9月份中国黄金储备连续第五个月保持不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fifth-straight-month-september-2024-10-07/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，中国央行9月份连续第五个月停止购买黄金作为储备，主要是由于黄金价格飙升。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fifth-straight-month-september-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>10年期国债收益率触及4%，抑制股市多头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-07/</link><description>上周美国劳动力市场数据消除了人们对经济衰退的担忧，推动降息押注减少，并至少在最初阶段支撑了美元和股市，周一基准10年期国债收益率升至4%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 00:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-07/</guid></item><item><title>台湾前总统蔡英文将进行敏感的布拉格访问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-tsai-make-sensitive-prague-visit-sources-say-2024-10-07/</link><description>台湾总统办公室周一表示，台湾前总统蔡英文将于本月访问捷克共和国，对于北京多次谴责为“分裂分子”的一位高级政治家来说，这是一次敏感的访问。</description><pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 00:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-tsai-make-sensitive-prague-visit-sources-say-2024-10-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>